'''克尔曼沙赫'''(Kermanshah; {{lang-fa|{{audio|fa-Kermanshah.ogg|کرمانشاه|help=no}}}}; {{lang-ku|Kirmaşan ,کرماشان}})是[[伊朗伊斯兰共和国|伊朗伊斯兰共和国]][[克尔曼沙赫省|克尔曼沙赫省]]的[[首府|省会]]，距[[首都|首都]][[德黑兰|德黑兰]]西偏南方向约525[[公里|公里]]（326英里），距离伊朗和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]边境约120公里。2005年估算[[人口|人口]]822,921<ref name="Cities in Iran">{{cite web | url =http://www.mongabay.com/igapo/2005_world_city_populations/Iran.html | title =Cities in Iran | year =2005 | accessdate =2008-04-04 | archive-date =2015-12-26 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20151226134415/http://www.mongabay.com/igapo/2005_world_city_populations/Iran.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>，2016年的人口普查，當地人口為946,681人（2019年的估計則為1,016,000人）。大多數當地人口操{{link-en|南庫爾德語|Sounthern Keudish}}。當地氣候溫和多山。<ref name="assistnews1">{{cite web |url=http://www.assistnews.net/Stories/2010/s10020115.htm |title=Arrest of the Assyrian leader of the Kermanshah Church in iran |publisher=Assistnews.net |accessdate=2011-12-02 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929225150/http://www.assistnews.net/Stories/2010/s10020115.htm |archivedate=2011-09-29 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.iranchamber.com/cities/kermanshah/kermanshah.php Iran Chamber society] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iranchamber.com/cities/kermanshah/kermanshah.php |date=20170202012439 }}: accessed: September 2010.</ref><ref name="zaban">[http://www.salamkermanshah.ir/test/kermanshah-mad-info.htm روزنامه سلام کرمانشاه] {{Wayback|url=http://www.salamkermanshah.ir/test/kermanshah-mad-info.htm |date=20100621084030 }} '''Persian''' ('''Kurdish''')</ref><ref name="b">[http://www.artkermanshah.ir/Default.aspx?page=3688 آشنایی با فرهنگ و نژاد استان کرمانشاه] {{Wayback|url=http://www.artkermanshah.ir/Default.aspx?page=3688 |date=20180901161010 }}('''Persian''')</ref><ref name=a>[http://www.kermanshahmiras.ir/fa_site/Preview.asp?categoryid=5&code=6686 سازمان میراث فرهنگی، صنایع دستی و گردشگری استان کرمانشاه] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kermanshahmiras.ir/fa_site/Preview.asp?categoryid=5&code=6686 |date=20180929020334 }} بازدی